&lt;h2 id="my-reaction"&gt;My Reaction&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Team Fortress 2 works because every class gives you something clear to do, and then throws you into matches where everything is happening at once. You are dodging rockets, chasing objectives, trying to stay alive and relying on teammates at the same time.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>